owDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"白金同學，感覺作為學生會長也開始變得更加可靠了。\n湊同學的話，雖然很直接但是很強勁的訊息呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"亞子","body":"對吧！？\n亞子聽了友希那學姊的話，全身都發麻了～！\n「你們，有為音樂賭上一切的覺悟嗎？」……像這樣！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"等等。\n請不要學我","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"亞子也很帥氣喔，\n我因為你說可以跟現在的團員演奏很開心，\n而相當感動呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"這是值得那麼感動的事嗎。\n我覺得只是把所想的事情說出來而已呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"我們的樂團，有發生過很多辛苦的艱難的事情。\n但是，無論何時我們都一起度過了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"正因為是跟這樣的你們一起，\n才能夠邁向往後新的未來。\n我是這麼想的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"友希那……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev109-ep2-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"這之後，想必也會有新的樂團出現。\n我們為了不輸給他們，\n今後也必須要目標走向更高峰才行呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionC